{"tid":2505342,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"[P仔入黎] Portal Reloaded Programming 問題","createTime":"2021-04-26T13:33:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-26T13:34:53.000Z","uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"61be576d161a883570ffd62e69448efdbb495ed6","tid":2505342,"uid":257658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"是咁的.<br />\nPortal 2 十周年. 有班外國人出左隻mod. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n多左一個新Portal. 叫Time Portal. (綠色)<br />\n<img src=\"https://assets2.rockpapershotgun.com/portal-reloaded.jpg/BROK/resize/1920%3E/format/jpg/quality/80/portal-reloaded.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fassets2.rockpapershotgun.com%2Fportal-reloaded.jpg%2FBROK%2Fresize%2F1920%253E%2Fformat%2Fjpg%2Fquality%2F80%2Fportal-reloaded.jpg&h=50b5b32d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經過Time Portal 就會去返20年後既同一位置. <br />\n所以現在可以改變未來. 都可以未來返回現在.<br />\n你依家郁既物件(下圖既方塊) 未來20年後都會係同一位置.<br />\n因為Test chamber 係無人理, 所以20年後會變到好鬼舊. <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZEGaqs7CthdSm5e34WuHNMkwYptiJXtvALwVHssJ9VCG?filename=UHZb7Wx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUHZb7Wx.png&h=5158f9bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我唔劇透. 只講第一關.<br />\nFor example: 你依家被困, 而你面前既鐵門會係20年後開返<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sweat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmRdeGZBzuNV6LKLSHR8sJ1csGVECYdXcMMWRAR8Nq1ubp?filename=ojevDQX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FojevDQX.png&h=141ba255&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n當然你都可以用Time Portal 去到20年後. 原來度門20年後已經爛左. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n走過去就過關啦. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmdKaACXFmXu3rHBoD8GKeatkLHKGgqHwc9AqPFq2QeFi3?filename=MDxQDRs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMDxQDRs.png&h=d1086de6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n為左方便分辦. 20年前後 會有好大分別. <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmbQcK8ybdVWvj4mnPhngpCsx8RgzGiWHzjzrAvkNNxPjJ?filename=1e5rcbW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1e5rcbW.png&h=304436e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一路寫code. 其實唔難啦. 分兩間房姐. <br />\n現在劉江華(x,y,z) = 20年後劉江華(x,y,z) <br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmQJWaLRmrrsCHWXwUsF5pxTWteEdV3xmDGx8FVGd3RTPH?filename=S9uC3Fe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9uC3Fe.png&h=b6a1d124&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n橙 藍Portal都寫好.<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAvAn0xY.gif&amp;h=3a4ecdf7&amp;s=540\" /><br />\ncurrent[x,y,z] = future[x,y,z]<br />\n<br />\n我第二間房整到殘殘舊舊就得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/plan.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 收工.<br />\n但點知岩岩打機出事 其實後面Time portal後面係咩都無.<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcnYar5KSdyVoUSic7kAFt1kvhXVcbSm7YBMD9Ss5H8E2?filename=o3RYNQY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo3RYNQY.png&h=3459ab01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n代表其實由頭到尾, 其實都係一間房??<br />\n<br />\n問題一: 大家覺得係咪由頭到尾都係一間房?<br />\n問題二: Any idea 一過time portal d野會變舊晒.<br />\n以我所知應該係落Post processing + shader寫到佢而表咁舊?<br />\n木板 地板可以咁樣寫. 但Props呢? 佢係連Props都唔同位.<br />\n爛晒既地板. 有部份位置唔同晒.<br />\n<br />\n藍橙Portal都寫好. Feel到呢個真係幾難.<br />\n希望有高手指導下. <img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n未玩過/仲唔明既朋友可以睇呢個.<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ID6HAaLSGD8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FID6HAaLSGD8&d=90j3dNidiaWpDV5wjwn%2B6xZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=f1e22428\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ID6HAaLSGD8</a>"},{"pid":"a131467537c0afa342b97a907fe1db6342001616","tid":2505342,"uid":343544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-26T13:34:53.000Z","msg":"有啲titanfall2嗰隻feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}